title: Alchemy 2021 — Puzzle Game

creator: Pavel Ilyin
descriptionHtml:
Take on the role of an aspiring alchemist. Your teacher has succeeded in harnessing the four basic elements: fire, water, earth, and air. By mixing these elements, you'll be able to unlock all the recipes you need to uncover the secrets of alchemy.

Create combinations using two or three elements (you can use elements twice). Recipes might be based on science (water + fire = steam) or on a set of symbols (fish + fountain = whale).

- More than 350 recipes.
- A stunning, colorful visual style.
- Ad-free gameplay. Free hints every six minutes.
- The ability to suggest your own recipes and correct translations directly in the game.
- Available in ten languages, including English.
- Adapted for the visually impaired.
descriptionShort: Combine elements and unlock new recipes!

descriptionHtml:
Take on the role of an aspiring alchemist. Your teacher has succeeded in harnessing the four basic elements: fire, water, earth, and air. By mixing these elements, you'll be able to unlock all the recipes you need to uncover the secrets of alchemy. Inventions and potions, animals and plants and much more interesing things!

Create combinations using two or three elements (you can use every element twice or thrice). Recipes might be based on science (water + fire = steam) or on a set of symbols (fish + fountain = whale).

- More than 400 recipes.
- Classic Alchemy game mechanics.
- A stunning, colorful visual style.
- Ad-free gameplay. Free hints every seven minutes.
- The ability to suggest your own recipes.
- Adapted for the visually impaired.
